Weijian’s PAG Asia 1 Fund Raises More Than $1.7 Billion, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-11T19:55:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/weijian-s-pag-asia-1-fund-raises-more-than-1-7-billion-ft-says.html
Pacific Alliance Group’s Shan Weijian has raised more than $1.7 billion for a new fund, PAG
Asia 1, which plans to invest in  China , the Financial Times
reported, without attribution.  To contact the reporter on this story:
